comments: Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact with Bullock (NYK) at the end of the drive as he turns to face the basket prior to his shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Burks (NYK) while defending the dribble handoff.
Harris (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball.
Harris' (PHI) off-hand makes marginal contact with Bullock's (NYK) backside as he changes direction during the drive.
Bullock (NYK) places a forearm on Harris' (PHI) front during Harris' drive to the basket and shot attempt, he does not extend or deliver any contact.
Burks (NYK) legally contest Simmons (PHI) shot at the basket.
Curry (PHI) makes marginal contact with Randle's (NYK) arm prior to the pass.
Thybulle (PHI) does not make any contact with Barrett (NYK) during Barrett's play at the basket.
Burks (NYK) makes marginal contact with Curry's (PHI) arm on the rip-through.
Burks (NYK) legally defends Curry's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) release his arm and makes marginal contact with Harris's (PHI) body during the rebound.
Barrett (NYK) makes contact with Simmons' (PHI) arm during his play at the basket.
Randle (NYK) initiates marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) at the end of the drive.
As Harris (PHI) jumps and opens up, allowing Randle (NYK) space to pass, Harris' arm slides across Randle's backside but does not impede his progress.
After the gather, Randle (NYK) becomes airborne to pass and his feet return to the floor prior to the release of his pass.
Harris (PHI) cleanly taps the ball away from Randle (NYK) during the rebound.
Randle (NYK) and Harris (PHI) make mutual marginal contact with one another during the rebound.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Randle (NYK) commits a take foul on Korkmaz (PHI).
Randle's (NYK) arm becomes interlocked with Curry's (PHI) arm as they engage during the screen.
Following the screen during the inbound play, Randle (NYK) continues to stay engaged with Curry (PHI) and clamps Curry's arm during the pick and affects his ability to defend.
Curry (PHI) legally contests Quickley's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) makes contact with Randle's (NYK) arm and affects his ability to pass.
Bullock (NYK) steps out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to PHI.
Barrett's (NYK) hand makes clean contact with the ball.
